data.description: Introducing 8859 Gelderland Way: a 2017-built, Taylor Morrison home in the award-winning Elk Grove School District. Boasting 4 beds, 3 full baths, and a generous 2548 sq ft, this popular Wayne floor plan is a marvel of modern design. As you step inside, be greeted by a grand foyer with soaring ceilings and custom laminate flooring, setting the tone for luxury living. A downstairs bedroom and bath offer convenience, while the separate living and family rooms provide ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. OWNED SOLAR panels adorn the roof, keeping energy costs low and eco-friendly. The heart of the home is the chef's dream kitchen featuring maple cabinets, granite countertops, and gleaming stainless-steel appliances.The whole-house EcoWater treatment system guarantees fresh, pure water at every turn. The front and backyard are professionally landscaped for tranquility and play. A gazebo and shed offer endless possibilities for relaxation and storage. Conveniently located near major shopping centers, Jimmie Yee Park, Wolfe Heights Winery and the 99 freeway. Do not miss out, schedule your showing today and step into your future home!
